   Roecklein J 1987 pp 389 [USE, DRA, TEXT]
   Nair P 1980 pp 301 [USE]
   Hornok L 1992 pp 162-166 [TEMP, RAIN, LIG, DRA, TEXT, USE]
   Small E (pers. comm.)

